data.description: **MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED: BEST & FINAL OFFERS DUE 4/23 @12pm!!** Welcome to 167 Franklin Ave in West Berlin NJ. This home was completely renovated in 2019 and includes all the major updates from a beautiful new kitchen with high-end granite countertops,  huge granite island, and stainless steel appliances. Updated bathrooms, flooring, carpeting, moldings, trim, lighting, and custom blinds. The main level has an open concept design, with a bonus space to put an office or playroom. The second floor features three bedrooms, and a very spacious full bathroom. Plus an unfinished attic and unfinished basement that could easily be converted into more living space or storage. Outside you will find a newly PVC fenced backyard, with a new shed. And let’s not forget about the freshly stained wrap around porch to enjoy a nice cup of coffee on in the morning! When the home was renovated in 2019, the electric service was also updated with a 200 amp service, new high energy efficient gas heater, new air conditioner and a new hot water heater. A brand new French drain system was installed in 2020, and a brand new roof installed in 2022. This house truly has all the bells and whistles. You do not want to miss the opportunity to own this beautiful home, book your appointment now, before it’s gone!!
